🥩🥪We just made the bomb Philly Cheese Steak Sammie!!🥩🥪 Stuffed with tons of different cheeses and Steak- it was a flavour explosion in our mouth!❤️❤️⁣
⁣
Ingredients:⁣
❤️Tenderloin ⁣
❤️Salt⁣
❤️Pepper⁣
❤️Loaf of bread⁣
❤️A mixture of shredded cheddar, mozzarella, peppery jack, red cheddar, Colby jack and Nacho cheese (it’s up to you)⁣
❤️2 tbsp butter, melted⁣
❤️Herbs ⁣
⁣
Steps:⁣
1)Sous vide tenderloin at 130F for 45mins. Pat dry steak and season with salt and pepper then pan fry in frying pan for 45secs on each side. Remove from pan and let rest for 30mins before slicing⁣
2)Slice open bread and brush with melted butter and herbs then TOP with your favourite cheeses.⁣
3)Bake in oven at 210C for 5mins until cheese has melted and is bubbly and golden brown⁣
4)Remove bread from oven and top with sliced steak and nacho cheese sauce⁣
5)Return to oven and bake for additional 5mins⁣
6)Best eaten immediately!!!⁣
⁣
Omg so good!!! The tenderloin was from @foodiemarketplacesg ❤️We find their meat reasonably priced and 👍🏻⁣
